snippet.textDisplay: I am a Pakistani from Punjab and I want to say to the Ayi Ayi Team that thanks to all of you for this struggle, this effort, going beyond the possible, in order to show us these beautiful people and their culture.. for us Sindh is Karachi and Hyderabad mostly.. we have no idea about the cultural elegance and richness beyond those cities.. thankyou for this glimpse.. thankyou for your good intentions and hardwork..we owe you all for this 🤎 May your song touches the heights of glory. Ameen 🙌
